summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 20757, entitled "An Ordinance providing for the laying off, widening, altering and establishing of Lakeside Avenue, from East Jefferson Street to Lake Dell Avenue; and providing for the changing of the use of said Lakeside Avenue, from East Jefferson Street to Lake Dell Avenue; and providing for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of land and other property necessary therefor; and providing that the payment for the same be made from the Park Fund of the City of Seattle.," approved April 26, 1909.
